# Optional: force this URL (e.g. staging server or Expo tunnel + ngrok to your API).
# EXPO_PUBLIC_API_FORCE_ENV=1
# EXPO_PUBLIC_API_URL=https://staging-api.example.com

# Release / EAS builds: if EXPO_PUBLIC_API_URL is unset, the app uses https://api.burqan.store (see resolveApiBase.ts).

# In development on a real phone, the app prefers the SAME host as Metro (from the JS bundle URL)
# on port 4000 — so you usually do NOT need EXPO_PUBLIC_API_URL unless you use `expo start --tunnel`
# or the API runs on another machine.

# If you still want a fixed URL in dev without FORCE, uncomment (use your machine's real LAN IP):
# EXPO_PUBLIC_API_URL=http://192.168.1.42:4000
